column5: you got to try this!  http://www.dontshootyoureyeout.com/
Thats a funny one my 6 yr old daughter just loved it !!!   she was playing it for 1/2 hour.....

I dont mean to brag or anything buuuuuuuttttt...  I got bored pretty quick and decided to see how many times I could shoot my self in the eye.  with 13 accidencts, and  325 bounces in one round I some how managed to earn the title "Fastest gun in the West".  high score of 6,407,909 points  Whats your high score?
I just had a wild bounce...took me to 9 million and change.. gave me 8 more bullets and then the counter rolled over and I ended with only 110,000 points. Some flaws in the free enjoyment !
